                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "walk_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Ah. The Sango non-signer. Yes, we heard. Declines get their own folder — thinner paper, thicker file. You are in it twice already, which for a person with no name is honestly impressive."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Nothing personal. I paste, they file, the folder grows. If you have a grievance about the postings, the channels remain: a fee, a fight, or the road."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Canvasser — the declines folder",
                    Label: "census_refused"
                },
                {
                    Priority: 10,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Answer for the postings",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    ConditionDataSet: {
                                        ConditionDataSet: [
