                            ],
                            Label: "walk_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Afternoon, resident. Company canvass, Takehara district. I am posting Verified Trust, Verified Value notices at the gym, the overlook, and the bridge, and I would take it kindly if the local artwork stopped reappearing over them. Bad glue on the artwork. Ours is much better glue."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "If you have a grievance about the postings, there are channels. There is a fee for one channel and a fight at the end of another. Or you can move along and let a working man supersede some signage in peace."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Company Canvasser",
                    Label: "challenge"
                }
            ]
        },
